eviously rejected any negotiated settlement that falls short of Iran\u2019s \u201cunconditional surrender,\u201d insisting that Washington must play a role in determining the country\u2019s future leadership.Leavitt said the president would consider the mission complete when Iran can no longer threaten the United States, its troops or personnel in the Middle East.", "content": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "keywords": ["world"], "creator": ["agencies"], "language": "english", "country": ["saudi arabia"], "category": ["world"], "datatype": "news", "pubDate": "2026-03-07 03:29:48", "pubDateTZ": "UTC", "fetched_at": "2026-03-07 04:13:22", "image_url": "https://saudigazette.com.sa/saudigazette/uploads/images/2026/03/07/2673657.webp", "video_url": null, "source_id": "saudigazette", "source_name": "Saudi Gazette", "source_priority": 356263, "source_url": "https://saudigazette.com.sa", "source_icon": "https://n.bytvi.com/saudigazette.png", "sentiment": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "sentiment_stats": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_tag": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_region": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_org": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_summary": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "duplicate": false}, {"article_id": "7fd41c729a24fe8b783028a37107ff64", "link": "https://www.channelnewsasia.com/world/iran-war-tehran-airport-israel-strikes-new-wave-5978331", "title": "Israel announces new wave of 'broad-scale' strikes on Tehran, airport hit", "description": "US Central Command says more than 3,000 Iranian targets have been struck over the past week.", "content": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "keywords": ["world"], "creator": ["cna"], "language": "english", "country": ["afghanistan", "india", "singapore", "saudi arabia", "maldives", "japan", "united arab emirates", "malaysia", "china", "south korea", "north korea", "taiwan", "thailand", "pakistan", "mongolia", "indonesia", "