velopments in the region and their implications for regional and global security.In a separate call, the Saudi Crown Prince spoke with Recep Tayyip Erdog\u0306an and condemned the Iranian attacks targeting Turkey, reaffirming the Kingdom\u2019s support for the measures taken by Ankara to protect its security and territorial integrity.The two sides also discussed the impact of the ongoing military escalation in the region on international and regional security.Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman also received a phone call from Nikos Christodoulides, during which they discussed the latest regional developments and their implications for stability.Both sides emphasized their rejection of any actions that could undermine the security and stability of the region.", "content": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "keywords": ["\u0622\u062e\u0631 \u0627\u0644\u0627\u062e\u0628\u0627\u0631"], "creator": ["saudi gazette"], "language": "english", "country": ["saudi arabia"], "category": ["politics", "top"], "datatype": "news", "pubDate": "2026-03-07 03:14:51", "pubDateTZ": "UTC", "fetched_at": "2026-03-07 03:43:10", "image_url": "https://saudigazette.com.sa/saudigazette/uploads/images/2026/03/07/2673650.webp", "video_url": null, "source_id": "saudigazette", "source_name": "Saudi Gazette", "source_priority": 356263, "source_url": "https://saudigazette.com.sa", "source_icon": "https://n.bytvi.com/saudigazette.png", "sentiment": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "sentiment_stats": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_tag": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_region": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_org": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_summary": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "duplicate": false}, {"article_id": "9ee46b44ab0aa1585099153b38d1a3a6", "link": "https://www.alyaum.com/articles/6649069/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%AE%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85/%D9%87%D9%84-%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B3%D